
Overview of noun rift

The noun rift has 3 senses (first 1 from tagged texts)
                                           
1. (1) rift -- (a gap between cloud masses; "the sun shone through a rift in the clouds")
2. rift -- (a narrow fissure in rock)
3. rupture, breach, break, severance, rift, falling out -- (a personal or social separation (as between opposing factions); "they hoped to avoid a break in relations")
